vulnerabilities.remediation:
Remove any invalid `ingress` block from the `aws_security_group` or `aws_default_security_group`.

Ensure that an [aws_default_security_group](https://registry.terraform.io/providers/hashicorp/aws/latest/docs/resources/default_security_group) or [aws_security_group](https://registry.terraform.io/providers/hashicorp/aws/latest/docs/resources/security_group) `ingress` block does NOT contain the value `0.0.0.0/0` in the `cidr_blocks` (`ipv6_cidr_blocks` for ipv6) field.

# Example configuration
```hcl
resource "aws_security_group" "example" {
  ingress {
    cidr_blocks = [10.0.0.0/16]
    from_port   = 5900
    to_port     = 5900
    # other required fields here
  }
}
```

Reference the `aws_vpc` in an `aws_flog_log` `vpc_id` field.

# Example Configuration

```hcl
resource "aws_vpc" "valid_vpc" {
# other required fields here
}

resource "aws_flow_log" "test_flow_log" {
vpc_id         = "${aws_vpc.valid_vpc.id}"
# other required fields here
}
```

